{"tid":1426562,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］只差呢一步就贏啦!!!","createTime":"2019-08-07T02:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T03:20:09.000Z","uid":138291,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"18b7be3a67b105507d834a5121a17e992bda4975","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:50:56.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我都係標題黨。但fake咗大家入嚟，如果我咩橋都冇都唔係咁好意思。<br />\n<br />\n留意到有人喺港獨議題上仍然用東江水做文章，覺得香港並唔能夠自給自足。香港人自給自足嘅方法，梁天琦嘅競選政綱入面其實齊曬，差在有冇人做。但我想講嘅並唔係港獨，呢d深奧問題留比學者解決，我只係廢青。<br />\n<br />\n我諗到嘅係一個真正實質宣告港共管治失效嘅方法。並唔只係成班人入立會叫口號嗰隻，而係真正取代成個政府。個方法就係海水化淡。香港人搞海水化淡<span style=\"color: red;\">公投</span>（我希望係程序嚴謹，比得上立會選舉），而<span style=\"color: red;\">政府部門</span>按公投結果去撥款、覓地、估價，完全繞過現時政府高層去施政，<span style=\"color: red;\">架空林鄭管治團隊</span>。做到呢步就證明林鄭管治失效，而我地取代佢嘅團隊去施政，亦都可以立即成立臨時政府去處理相關事務。<br />\n<br />\n當然，問題係政府部門點會聽我地支旗。恕我廢青一個諗唔到咩好橋，唯有希望大家都幫下手集思廣益。我盡咗力啦，屌細力d唔該。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後：<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2304b9e6591525864fc327955b33fe3acd4e12e9","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:51:43.000Z","msg":"可以係其他施政議題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b164a0d8fcdfd1b94b4324247ad1995175a17d6","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:51:56.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"c330d7e2cb7f15a22940f1049cbd76b805017028","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:52:06.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"1c4729c8b3490e3a646958bc48d3572c590b94b3","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:52:22.000Z","msg":"大家覺得得唔得"},{"pid":"973c9aa4f24f10c7946f670239d0b32de1e380b2","tid":1426562,"uid":264457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:53:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"e947998906d5a7eafa930df237dfdaae1dcd20cf","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:53:47.000Z","msg":"我唔清楚點樣動用政府庫房，有冇人可以指點下？"},{"pid":"7dc3c173cad74b8d4ea3feff31fe2419a5a56f3b","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"973c9aa4f24f10c7946f670239d0b32de1e380b2","tid":1426562,"uid":264457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:53:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:54:20.000Z","msg":"對唔住fale咗你入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3c5ac9cb8104f563ea9b3f93185dd2fea86eee0","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b4e1dd03bc6debdbe750a7a61daa1846acdd6342","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:55:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />觀星激光槍biubiubiu!"},{"pid":"c51b0098a25ed98ea7ad4843014848cdd554301c","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"條橋真係咁曳？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a714b759935b6eb4620d35be5ba4e118274bc2e0","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:56:16.000Z","msg":"諗唔過呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698d1067803a86fd455156fa918f12255e6d35b8","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"入一入嚟話比我知有咩問題都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6f18483ee64a3a2c8e22eafc4e43d62c6e3a53","tid":1426562,"uid":138291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"